title: (J-POP) Galileo Galilei Discography
description:
A collection of Galileo Galilei music.

Included are:
Alarms
Ame Nochi Galileo
Aoi Shiori
Asu E
Baby, It's Cold Outside
Boku Kara Kimi E
Circle Game
Hamanasu no Hana
Natsuzora
Parade
Portal
Sayonara Frontier
Yotsuba Sagashi no Tabibito

I would recommend changing the language locale of your computer to preserve the Japanese text, but this is not required.
Some music files have been downloaded without the locale and thus the Japanese is gibberish, but the music file info should be fine (so their names should be normal in iTunes.)

Please seed and enjoy.
